      (a) is intended to generate revenue, profit, or other commercial
          advantage for You or any third party;
      (b) involves operating the Software or any Derivative Work as a service
          accessible to third parties for a fee, subscription, or any form of
          monetary or non-monetary consideration;
      (c) involves incorporating the Software or any Derivative Work into any
