          or otherwise monetized;
      (d) involves using the Software to support or facilitate any commercial
          operation, enterprise, or business activity;
      (e) involves using the Software in a for-profit organization's internal
          operations, even if end users are not charged directly; or
      (f) provides any form of indirect commercial benefit, including but not
          limited to attracting users, investment, advertising revenue, or
