        internally within a single natural person's private household, strictly
        for personal use, provided:
          (i)   the instance is inaccessible to any person other than that
                natural person;
          (ii)  no fee or consideration of any kind is charged to any user;
          (iii) no commercial activity whatsoever is supported by the instance;
          (iv)  the instance does not constitute or operate as a Competing
                Product or Service; and
          (v)   no more than one (1) private instance is operated at any time.

    (f) FREE PUBLIC NON-COMMERCIAL HOSTING: Deploy and operate a publicly
        accessible instance of the Software, provided that ALL of the
        following conditions are met without exception:
          (i)   No fee, subscription, donation solicitation, paid tier,
                premium feature, or any other form of monetary or non-monetary
                consideration is charged to or collected from any user in
