                as they appear in the Software, unmodified and unobscured, in
                all user-facing interfaces and in the source code;
          (v)   The instance is not presented as a distinct or independent
                product — it must be clearly identified to all users as running
                SigmaGit with a visible link to the official SigmaGit repository;
          (vi)  The instance does not offer functionality, integrations, or
                modifications that are designed to or have the effect of
                commercially differentiating it from the official SigmaGit
                platform;
          (vii) You provide the Licensor with written notice of the public
